  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl, whisk together lime juice, fish sauce, sugar, salt, and black pepper for the pickling liquid.",
    "Slice the cucumber into thin rounds.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix together the mayonnaise, chili sauce, and 1 tablespoon of the pickling liquid.",
    "Add the sliced cucumber to the bowl with the mayonnaise mixture and toss to coat.",
    "In another bowl, mix the pickling liquid with the sliced carrots and let sit for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Once the pork shoulder is cooked, slice it thinly against the grain.",
    "Assemble the sandwich by spreading the mayonnaise mixture on the bánh mì bread, followed by the sliced pork, sous-vide egg, pickled carrots, and fresh basil."
